The '''2020 [[European Women's Handball Championship]]''' will be held in [[Denmark]] and [[Norway]] in 2020. The games will be played in [[Herning]], [[Denmark]] and [[Stavanger]], [[Trondheim]] and [[Oslo]], [[Norway]]. The preliminary rounds will be played in Herning and Trondheim, the main round in Herning and Stavanger and the finals in Oslo.<ref name="EHF"/>
